          p.text.text--14 CLEANSING MILK PLEASURE is an ultra-thin cleansing milk and makeup remover designed for use on sensitive skin. This gentle but thorough cosmetic product deeply cleanses the skin, calming and toning the cellular tissue of the skin. In addition, the product smoothes delicate skin surfaces. It provides the skin with a full and long-lasting moisturizing effect, penetrating the skin layers for moisturizing. Moreover, the product softens the growth of new cells. Highly effective and pure ingredient of white lotus extract extracted from a beautiful lotus flower. The extract is widely known and appreciated for its purity and excellent cleansing properties. During cleansing, this unique formula also balances and evens out skin tones for a radiant youthful effect.

          h4.text.text--14-medium Recommended skin cleansing directions

          p.text.text--14 Recommended directions for using this clean, anti-aging skincare product are to apply a small amount of this specialized cleanser both morning and evening, gently massaging, but thoroughly, on the face, neck and décolleté. Allow extra time to massage any area of ​​dry, oily, oily, or sun-damaged skin. Rinse your skin thoroughly with warm or cold water using cotton swabs, and then wipe dry with a fresh cosmetic towel or clean, soft cloth.
          
