            p.text.text--14 When developing this revitalizing collection of cosmetics, Andrey Shor included pure natural ingredients that can deal with such harmful environmental factors as ultraviolet radiation, climate change, pollution from vehicles and factories, stress from everyday life, and even interfere with them. fluctuations in blood pressure and dehydration of skin tissue caused by dry or overheated rooms.

          p.text.text--14 This excellent collection of cosmetics restores and supports the natural processes of the production and regeneration of the skin, preventing its aging. This healthy collection of pure cosmetics gives the skin vitality, youth and attractiveness. When used daily, CLEANSING MILK PLEASURE will help your skin look and feel younger, brighter and healthier.

